products.title: Building Better - Sustainable Architecture for Family Homes
products.body_html:
Sustainability and energy efficiency play a critical role for anyone building or renovating a house. Thankfully, architects from around the world are now developing single-family homes that combine ecological responsibility with contemporary and imaginative design. Building Better is an engaging visual showcase of outstanding environmentally friendly houses. products.title: Shoes Like Pottery (High Top - Natural)
products.body_html:
*Sizing Note: These sneakers run large. We suggest sizing down one size

As the Shoes Like Pottery name implies, these sneakers are fired in a kiln at 120°c for 70 minutes using the ancient Japanese “ka-ryu” process. This special vulcanization process causes the sulfur and raw rubber to chemically react and return the rubber to its natural elasticity. The result is an incredible soft, flexible, comfortable sole. Kiln firing also gives each pair a unique texture and finish similar to artisan Japanese ceramics.

The “ka-ryu” process, which is only performed by a handful of manufacturers around the world, fuses the rubber outsole to the canvas upper, making them super durable to withstand lots of wear.

Features:

  • Handmade in Kurume, Japan
  • Vulcanized sole made using the kiln-firing "Ka-ryu" process
  • Canvas upper
  • Rubber toe cap
  • Cushioned in-sole
  • Reinforced toe and heel
  • Brass eyelets
  • Hand-stamped rubber seal

products.title: Bolt Action Pen (Brass)
products.body_html:
We partnered with our friends at Inventery to make special edition Ugmonk Bolt Action Pens.

Each pen is precision-machined from raw brass stock using a single tungsten blade. The Ugmonk logo is diamond-etched on the metal clip. The bolt action mechanism allows you to quickly click the pen in and out with either hand and creates an audible snap.

The Schmidt P8126 Capless System roller ball refill is a favorite among pen enthusiasts. The 0.6mm stainless steel fine tip allows the quick-drying liquid ink to flow smoothly on the page.

INVENTERY Fine Writing Instruments are covered by a lifetime warranty and guarantee against all mechanical failure and defects in materials or workmanship.

Features:

  • Material: Untreated Brass
  • Weight: 53g
  • Length: 13cm / 5.125"
  • Diameter: 10.4mm
  • Compatible with Schmidt P8126 (included) & Parker style refills
  • Diamond Etched Ugmonk logo
  • Warranted through Inventery
